Anyone have an idea of making this shield stunning script more consistant when on 80ms+
def module shield-stun
def desc "Activates after hitting a blocking enemy — switches to axe and double-hits to stun"

on damage if playing {
    as target_entity if blocking {
        if hotbar_has #axe {
            wait 0.05 switch #axe
            wait 0.05 input attack
            wait 0.05 input attack
            wait 0.1 switch back
        }
    }
}